name: Panic at the Disco  Tree V3

metadata.name: Panic! at the Disco | Tree
metadata.description:
This was shot at a time on our career when we were photographing a lot of “up and coming” musicians for AOL. The AOL headquarters were located in a generic office building in Beverly Hills. At the time, the trees in front of that building were in full bloom and the colors worked perfectly for this shot.
Location: Beverly Hills, CA
